---
title: Barramundi in Brown Butter-Lemon Sauce with Roasted Potatoes and Green Beans
description: For tonight's feast, you'll whip up pan-fried, flaky barramundi, roasted potatoes and lemony green beans, all covered in a velvety brown butter-lemon sauce. If this sounds complicated –it’s not! 30 minutes is all it takes for this dish to land on your table.
